2007-06-11  Vincent Untz  <vuntz@gnome.org>

	Make VnckPager and VnckTasklist always display the screen they're on.
	This deprecates vnck_pager_set_screen() and
	vnck_tasklist_set_screen(), and also makes the screen argument of
	vnck_pager_new() and of vnck_tasklist_new() useless.

	* libvnck/pager.c: (vnck_pager_finalize): don't disconnect from the
	screen. That's done in vnck_pager_unrealize() now.
	(_vnck_pager_set_screen): new helper to automatically set the screen,
	based on what vnck_pager_set_screen() was doing
	(vnck_pager_realize): document a bit, and set the screen if it wasn't
	set before
	(vnck_pager_unrealize): disconnect the screen
	(vnck_pager_size_request): set the screen if it wasn't set before
	(vnck_pager_set_screen): deprecate
	(vnck_pager_new): don't call vnck_pager_set_screen()
	(vnck_pager_set_layout_hint): set the screen if it wasn't set before.
	It's useful if users are calling set_n_rows() before the widget is
	shown.
	(vnck_pager_set_orientation): don't reset orientation in case of
	failure if we didn't know about our screen before we tried changing
	the layout (and thus didn't know about the real orientation)
	(vnck_pager_set_n_rows): don't reset n_rows in case of failure if we
	didn't know about our screen before we tried changing the layout (and
	thus didn't know about the real n_rows)
	(vnck_pager_connect_screen): we don't need the screen argument here
	(vnck_pager_disconnect_screen): small update
	* libvnck/tasklist.c: (vnck_tasklist_finalize): don't disconnect from
	the screen. That's done in vnck_tasklist_unrealize() now.
	(vnck_tasklist_realize): do what the vnck_tasklist_set_screen() used
	to do 
	(vnck_tasklist_unrealize): disconnect from the screen
	(vnck_tasklist_connect_screen): we don't need a screen argument here
	(vnck_tasklist_set_screen): deprecated
	(vnck_tasklist_new): don't call vnck_tasklist_set_screen()
	(vnck_tasklist_update_lists): don't do anything if the widget is not
	realized yet, which means we don't know about our screen.
	* libvnck/screen.c: (vnck_screen_get_workspace): add soft assertion
	(vnck_screen_get_workspace_index): add soft assertion
	(vnck_screen_get_workspace_neighbor): add soft assertion
	(vnck_screen_net_wm_supports): add soft assertion
	(vnck_screen_release_workspace_layout): add soft assertion

